query:
SELECT w.id as workspaceId, w.name as workspaceName, wi.id as instanceId, wi.instanceKey, wi.status 
FROM whatsapp_instances wi 
JOIN workspaces w ON wi.workspaceId = w.id 
LIMIT 1
